<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>『one』</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>茶底·维他奶+巧克力酱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201205/30035f7a96c045d6b32cb7e7c70124e1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201205/30035f7a96c045d6b32cb7e7c70124e1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201205/20a236ced5cc42f0bcd60cbc41c2ed3e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201205/20a236ced5cc42f0bcd60cbc41c2ed3e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">奶底用的是<strong>维他奶</strong>，奶香味更浓郁和细腻，加上香浓的巧克力酱混合做成厚乳冰，<strong>入口甜度刚好不腻不齁</strong>，光靠奶底就能把巧克力控拿捏得死死地...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>『two』</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>加料·现熬黑糖珍珠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201205/9b09eabc40ce4375937023f85d7b29a9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>===</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201205/9d55d1b77c064263bfe32c37ff4ec627.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">沙冰最底下的黑糖珍珠是精髓。每天现熬现做，软韧适中，外表还包裹着糖浆，<strong>随着冰沙一口吸进嘴里，我开始怀念夏日了</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>『three』</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>封顶·厚奶塔+酷脆碎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201205/e6695648952649759653e7e67887dfca.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201205/7a01213a2aff42b59b16381f3451a3bf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201205/9d5f55afd9f147789611c22881bd22df.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最惊的是这厚乳塔，吃一层就快饱了...顶上还撒了一层酷脆碎，挖着吃最爽！<strong>一口绵滑一口香脆</strong>，乘风破浪的本姐姐也爱得不要不要地...</p>
