<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>牛肉丸粿条汤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>●GUANG NAN NIU WAN</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201206/1ffd51b6c4084b96b8cfd9c0a5753333.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">潮汕人的一日三餐：<strong>非粿条莫属</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛肉丸在锅中翻滚着</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不用加太多调料也能尝到<strong>鲜美</strong></p>
