<p class="ql-align-justify">牛肉丸烤着吃都绝了！端上来的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有点<strong>日式居酒屋的烧鸟既视感</strong>呢！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201206/8eb5a5746f1d428bb061c9d21a52c91f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">牛肉丸上面撒上佐料</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">烤好的牛肉丸</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">依然保持Q弹</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">也<strong>别有一番滋味</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>椒盐牛肉丸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201206/8aacfddf21fe4d21944e810c9c2b2b3b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在慵懒的晚上，可以准备点牛肉丸，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">打花后直接油炸，撒上<strong>椒盐粉</strong>混合在一起，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">做个小加餐</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>肉感十足的牛肉丸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">搭配<strong>咸香的椒盐</strong>，好像还不赖...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201206/7ac734c9c4214e39bd5b8ea84061f2e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
