<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>猪肚丸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201206/44108d7021ee408eb2640713e6ce18c8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">猪肚丸延续牛肉丸的制作工艺</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">采用<strong>上等的潮汕猪肚以及新鲜猪腿肉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">再加入多种配料，<strong>“粗暴”搅打而成</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>柔软喷香，饱满得很有层次！</strong></p>
