<p class="ql-align-justify">深知其中之<strong>鲜甜，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">哪怕简单的水煮</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">都不会觉得乏味~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>虾枣</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201206/b260413f3135439699bfbd8ccd32e826.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每日一早采购的<strong>鲜虾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">是制作虾枣的主要食材</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">肥硕鲜美的虾采购完成后</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还需将其洗净，再剥壳去虾线~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">匠人的执着，是纯手工打造每一颗虾枣</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">剁虾肉、手工拍浆，再用勺子刮至成形</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Q弹的虾枣，就此孕育而生~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201206/dc44d868cf5b4007b8f55f8fcfaba430.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201206/dc44d868cf5b4007b8f55f8fcfaba430.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每颗虾枣出锅后<strong>色泽金黄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">只是看着就使人<strong>食欲大开</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">放进嘴里一口一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">真是鲜到不行</p>
